Entries.default: "Caed Nua looked a bit like this. After Eothas rose."
"Don't think about it, captain. Don't look in their eyes."
"I dreamt about this day. Dreamt about the screams, too."
"So many people discarded like refuse... We cannot forget what happened here."
"Magran's bleedin' fissures, this is not what I joined up for."
"You owe me a trip to the bathhouse after this. No, ten trips!"
"Ugh. This facility never lacked for raw material to experiment on."
"They are beyond feeling. Pity them not."
